Body:
```markdown
When osascript/defaults resolution fails due to bundle ID mismatch between LaunchServices (e.g., com.microsoft.edgemac) and Info.plist (e.g., com.microsoft.Edge), fall back to known paths for common Chromium browsers.

Fixes #48560
```

